<LanguageData>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] psychically suggested that [RECIPIENT_nameDef] keep up [RECIPIENT_possessive] guard, in preparation for a future attack.-->
  <HVP_WordOfWarning.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 초집중 암시로 [RECIPIENT_nameDef]에게 미래의 공격에 대비해 경계를 유지하라고 경고함.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfWarning.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] psychically hypnotized [RECIPIENT_nameDef] into a trancelike state.-->
  <HVP_WordOfContemplation.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 초집중 능력으로 [RECIPIENT_nameDef](을)를 황홀경 상태로 유도함.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfContemplation.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] bound a skipgate to [RECIPIENT_nameDef] that will rescue [RECIPIENT_objective] if at risk of death.-->
  <HVP_WordOfSafety.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 [RECIPIENT_nameDef]에게 죽음의 위협이 닥치면 구출해 줄 관문을 연결함.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfSafety.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] carefully skipped medical mechanites into the body of [RECIPIENT_nameDef] to cure an adverse health condition.-->
  <HVP_WordOfSterility.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 [RECIPIENT_nameDef]의 신체 내부로 치료용 기계입자들을 조심스럽게 순간이동시켜 유해한 건강 문제를 치료함.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfSterility.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] psychically melded [RECIPIENT_nameDef] into the consciousness of another.-->
  <HVP_WordOfMelding.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 [RECIPIENT_nameDef]의 정신을 다른 존재의 의식 속으로 융합시킴.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfMelding.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
  <!--Original=r_logentryー&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef] imbued [RECIPIENT_nameDef] with a potent psychic blessing.-->
  <HVP_WordOfBlessing.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
    <li>r_logentry-&gt;[INITIATOR_nameDef](이)가 [RECIPIENT_nameDef]에게 강력한 초능력 축복을 부여함.</li>
  </HVP_WordOfBlessing.logRulesInitiator.rulesStrings>
